item_category: This Stormforce gaming system is powered by the latest Intel 10th Gen technology that utilises the correct balance of clock speeds, cores and threads to offer game changing performance. At the heart of this system is the Intel Core i3-10100 core processor that can turbo up to an impressive 4.3GHz. Experience high performing multitasking support powered by 4 cores with Intel Hyper-Threading Technology (Intel HT Technology) that will ease you through any demanding workload.
